snippet.title: Jets'n'Guns for Nintendo Switch Trailer
snippet.description:
Hey! Enjoy the thrilling action in our classic side-scrolling shooter Jets'n'Guns on Nintendo Switch!

An evil mastermind and his crazy pirate army emerge from the darkness and threaten to destroy the whole universe! You are the only one standing between them and the total annihilation.

Go for a ride with this insane retro side scrolling space shooter with more than 40 levels, dozen of awesome spaceships to choose from, and more than 70 over the top weapons to equip in the war against the lunatic evil overlord!


#NintendoSwitch #Nintendo  #RetroGaming #jng #JetsnGuns #AlienShooter #SpaceShooter #IndieGame


Game's official site: http://www.rakeingrass.com/game_jetsnguns.php
